## Summary

| Comment Type | When to Use |
|--------------|-------------|
| **Inline (WHY)** | Business logic, workarounds, constraints |
| **JSDoc** | Public APIs, complex functions, reusable code |
| **Dividers** | Large files with multiple sections |
| **File headers** | Entry points, complex modules, libraries |
| **TODO/FIXME** | Technical debt, future improvements |

